			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc vellem<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Was <persName ref="64">Frecht</persName> zu Bullingers Brief vom 12. April 1545 (s. oben Anm. 1) zu sagen hatte.</note> meo nomine, si tua claritas ad Bullingerum scriberet, per occasionem ei significaret<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Vadian schickte am 8. Juli den ganzen an ihn gerichteten Brief <persName ref="64">Frechts</persName> an Bullinger weiter; s. unten <ref target="file#12239">Nr. 2192</ref>.</note> simulque gratias ageret, quod pro sua insigni et liberali in me benevolentia et humanitate misisset aliquot libellos<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Vgl. oben Anm. 1.</note> et pariter<pb type="edition" next="344"/> in proximis suis ad me rogasset et obtestatus esset, ne alienarem ego mentem meam ab eis<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">von den Zürchern.</note> propter quorundam<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Darunter u.a. <persName ref="28">Bucer</persName>, ein Korrespondent <persName ref="64">Frechts</persName>, was Bullinger bekannt war; vgl. unten <ref target="file#12240">Nr. 2193</ref>, 8-20.</note> contra ipsos maledicentiam - adiecta ista contestatione, quod tales ipsi non essent, quales illi pingerent eos -, et (quod mihi valde gratum fuit) adiecit: „Sumus sane homines.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Desunt nobis plurima, sed hic consilia et admonitione fratrum nunquam sprevimus neque porro despiciemus.“</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc Bullingerus...</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
